parameters:
Did you use teleportation magic to move? Are you
okay?

It's just us... Did Amelia and the others get sent
to a different place?
I am the master of this dungeon.
First, let me explain the rules.

Hey, don't proceed with the conversation on your
own. Return to the original place, please.

Once you open the grimoire, your participation is
decided.

If you don't clear it, you won't be able to leave
from here.
This is so boring, isn't it?
What are we going to do if we can't clear it?

There's no problem. It has become something that
anyone can clear.

From now on, challengers will have to fight
against me.

If you can achieve victory, you will be able to
proceed to the next room.

If you achieve victory three times, the dungeon
will be cleared.

I am the creator of this dungeon, imbued with the
magical power of the 386th representative of the
Magic Research Society.

I don't know, but they're not from a long time
ago.
I see... You seem fairly strong.

No way, I'm the representative of the Magic
Research Society, so obviously I'm super strong.
There's no way we can win against them.
There is not just one way to clear the dungeon.

If the two of you engage in naughty things
starting now, you can clear the game without
having to battle.

The challenge in this room is for a male to
ejaculate through a handjob.

So it's the Ecchi Dungeon... What a stupid thing
to create.

I know it's not the best thing to say, but... is
it no good?

Just because I'm a slut doesn't mean I'll do it
with anyone.
Besides, I'm not really in the mood right now.
I don't know if I can defeat it.
Please, fight alongside me at least.
Now, please proceed to the next room.

It's true... If it was just me and Elena, we would
have definitely lost.
Well then, let's go to the next room.
